  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Moss, run by our long-standing partner Imre, is a firm favourite with Inghams' guests year on year. The hotel has had a complete renovation and all rooms have been renovated to a high standard and have use of the hotel's new restaurant, bar, and indoor pool.</p>
<h2>Prime location</h2>
<p><span>The hotel is located in a quiet side street only two minutes’ walk from the nearest piste and ski school meeting point. </span>It’s convenient for lift access, being only five minutes’ walk from the Festkogel gondola leading to the entire <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/6063ab813f384ab795dc6aa1d337f576" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6063ab813f384ab795dc6aa1d337f576}" target="_blank" title="Obergurgl">Obergurgl</a>-<a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/5c5a68def0234451a0e7113b85bac993" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5c5a68def0234451a0e7113b85bac993}" target="_blank" title="Hochgurgl">Hochgurgl</a> area.</p>
<h2>Restaurant &amp; bar</h2>
<p>The new design concept uses natural materials and inspiration from the surrounding mountains. A warm, inviting atmosphere is found throughout the hotel and there is a small bar area which is the perfect place to chill in the evening with a drink.</p>
<h2>Indoor pool &amp; spa</h2>
<p>The hotel's renovations have added a new wellness area which includes an indoor swimming pool, sauna, and steam room. Massages and treatments are available to book locally.</p>
<h2>Rooms types for everybody</h2>
<p>The hotel is split into two wings. All rooms are newly renovated and decorated with local materials in a modern style. Choose from a variety of room types, from twins to larger suites sleeping up to six, perfect for families.</p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with the Moss the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>
<h3>Why is this an Inghams' Choice property?</h3>
<p><strong>Service</strong><span> </span>- We value the great partnerships we have with our hotels and our longstanding relationship with the Moss means we know you are getting the very best on your Inghams holiday.</p>
<p><strong>Refurbishment</strong>- For this season the Moss has undergone a full hotel renovation, adding an indoor pool and wellness area.</p>
<p><strong>Alpine chic</strong><span> </span>- You can feel like you're on the mountains without even leaving your hotel room. The alpine features and materials used at the Moss give it the perfect alpine feel throughout.</p>
<p><span>Photos: Stratus Hotels GmbH</span></p>]]></description>
