  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>First Floor</strong></p>
<p>Room 111 &amp; 112 are Austrian twins with showers, WC &amp; balconies</p>
<p>Room 113 Austrian twin with shower &amp; WC</p>
<p>Room 114 Austrian twin with shower, WC &amp; shared balcony</p>
<p>Suite 115 Austrian twin connecting to a separate room with bunk beds, shower, WC &amp; shared balcony</p>
<p>Room 116 Twin/Triple (Austrian twin &amp; single sofa bed) with shower, WC &amp; shared balcony. Suitable for 2 adults, or 2 adults and a child 16 years and under</p>
<p>Room 117 Is a small Austrian twin with shower, WC &amp; shared balcony</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Second Floor</strong></p>
<p>Room 121 &amp; 122 are Austrian twins with showers, WC &amp; balconies</p>
<p>Room 123 Austrian twin with shower &amp; WC</p>
<p>Room 124 Austrian twin with shower, WC &amp; shared balcony</p>
<p>Suite 125 Austrian twin connecting to a separate room with bunk beds, shower, WC &amp; shared balcony</p>
<p>Room 126 Twin/Triple (Austrian twin &amp; single sofa bed) with shower, WC &amp; shared balcony. Suitable for 2 adults, or 2 adults and a child 16 years and under</p>
<p>Room 127 Is a small Austrian twin with shower, WC &amp; shared balcony</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>The Moss Wing</strong></p>
<p>All Moss Wing rooms have balconies except for room 323.</p>
<p>Room 212, 221-23, 312-13 &amp; 321-22 are Austrian twins with showers and WC. They can sleep two adults. </p>
<p>Room 214, 224, 311 &amp; 323 are 19-25m² and can sleep 2 adults, or 2 adults and a child 16 years and under</p>
<p>Room 211 &amp; 213 are larger at 22-28m² and can sleep 2 adults, or 2 adults and a child 16 years and under</p>
<p>Room 215-17 &amp; 225-27 are 26-36m² and can sleep 2 adults and 2 children 16 years and under</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Second Floor Side Wing</strong></p>
<p>Suite 314 Sleeps 4-6 (Max. 5 adults) Two Austrian twin bedrooms, separate lounge with double sofa bed, three separate bathrooms with shower and WC, TV &amp; balcony. </p>
<p>Suite 315 &amp; Suite 316 Sleep 4-6 (Max. 5 adults) with Two Austrian twin bedrooms, separate lounge with double sofa bed, two separate bathrooms with shower and WC, TV &amp; balcony. </p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Shared balconies:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Room 114 balcony is shared with Suite 115</li>
<li>Room 116 balcony is shared with Room 117</li>
<li>Room 124 balcony is shared with Suite 125</li>
<li>Room 126 balcony is shared with Room 127</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Cable / satellite TV</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
